## Recode Update Rule (Compact)

For **every upgrade/change** made in this repo, immediately append one log entry to `doc/recode.md`.

Required fields per entry:
- `timestamp` (ISO format: `YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss Z`)
- `agent` (`codex` | `claude` | `copilot`)
- `github_username`
- `branch`
- `upgrade_paths` (comma-separated file paths changed)
- `upgrade_summary` (1-2 short lines)

Use this format:

```md
### [timestamp] agent=<codex|claude|copilot> user=<github_username> branch=<branch_name>
- upgrade_paths: path/a.ts, path/b.ts, path/c.ts
- upgrade_summary: what was upgraded and why.
```

